---
// AeonCircle — Live to 120 with AI
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>AeonCircle — Live to 120 with AI</title>
<meta name="description" content="AI-driven longevity. Real-time vitals, gene optimization, metabolic regulation, aging reversal, personalized life-extension protocols." />
<link rel="canonical" href="https://aeoncircle.com/" />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://aeoncircle.com/" />
<meta property="og:title" content="AeonCircle — Live to 120 with AI" />
<meta property="og:description" content="An AI-driven longevity system. Live to 120, by design." />
<meta property="og:site_name" content="AeonCircle" />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0A192F" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --space: #0A192F;
    --space-2: #0E2240;
    --space-3: #142B4F;
    --cyan: #64FFDA;
    --cyan-dim: rgba(100,255,218,0.55);
    --cyan-soft: rgba(100,255,218,0.10);
    --white: #F8FBFF;
    --white-2: #B8C8DC;
    --white-3: #7A8AA0;
    --purple: #9D4EDD;
    --line: rgba(248,251,255,0.10);
    --line-2: rgba(248,251,255,0.18);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--space);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ── Navigation ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 18px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    background: rgba(10,25,47,0.55);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .brand {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .brand-mark { width: 26px; height: 26px; color: var(--cyan); }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex; gap: 28px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white-2);
  }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--white-2); text-decoration: none;
    transition: color .2s;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--cyan); }
  .nav-links a.login {
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 120px 40px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── Section 1: Hero ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 140px 40px 80px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background:
      radial-gradient(1100px 700px at 50% 40%, rgba(100,255,218,0.10), transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(700px 600px at 80% 90%, rgba(157,78,221,0.06), transparent 60%),
      var(--space);
  }

  /* DNA particle / cell field — pure CSS+SVG, subtle motion */
  .dna-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.45;
  }
  .dna-bg svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
  .dna-bg .strand {
    stroke: var(--cyan);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 0.6;
    opacity: 0.35;
    animation: drift 40s linear infinite;
  }
  .dna-bg .strand-2 { animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 55s; stroke: rgba(157,78,221,0.4); }
  @keyframes drift {
    0%   { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(-160px); }
  }
  /* Floating cell dots */
  .cells { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .cells .cell {
    position: absolute;
    width: 4px; height: 4px;
    background: var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.4;
    animation: float linear infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(100,255,218,0.5);
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); opacity: 0; }
    10%  { opacity: 0.5; }
    90%  { opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-120vh) translateX(40px); opacity: 0; }
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 920px; }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
  }
  .hero-eyebrow .pulse {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    background: var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--cyan);
    animation: blink 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }
    50%      { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 112px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .hero h1 .with-ai {
    color: var(--cyan);
  }
  .hero-zh {
    font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 19px);
    color: var(--white-2);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.2vw, 15px);
    color: var(--white-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    max-width: 760px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex; gap: 18px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 16px 30px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    transition: all .3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan) 0%, #4FE0BD 100%);
    color: var(--space);
    border: 1px solid var(--cyan);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--cyan);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(100,255,218,0.25);
  }
  .btn-primary .arrow { transition: transform .3s ease; }
  .btn-primary:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  /* Scroll cue */
  .scroll-cue {
    position: absolute; bottom: 30px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: var(--white-3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .scroll-cue::after {
    content: ""; width: 1px; height: 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cyan) 0%, transparent 100%);
    animation: cueDrop 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes cueDrop {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; height: 28px; }
    50%      { opacity: 1; height: 44px; }
  }

  /* ── Section title (shared) ───────────────────────────────── */
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan); margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 56px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .section-title .accent { color: var(--cyan); }

  /* ── Section 2: Core Value (3 cards) ──────────────────────── */
  .system {
    background: var(--space);
  }
  .system::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(800px 500px at 50% 0%, rgba(100,255,218,0.04), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .system-container { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,251,255,0.025) 0%, rgba(248,251,255,0.005) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: border-color .3s ease, transform .3s ease, background .3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--cyan-dim);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(100,255,218,0.04) 0%, rgba(248,251,255,0.01) 100%);
  }
  .card-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 26px;
  }
  .card-num {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--cyan); opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .card h3 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .card p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--white-2);
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── Section 3: Science (left/right) ──────────────────────── */
  .science {
    background: var(--space-2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .science-container {
    max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .science-diagram { position: relative; }
  .science-diagram svg { width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .science-text .section-eyebrow { color: var(--cyan); }
  .science-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    color: var(--white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .science-text h2 .num { color: var(--cyan); }
  .science-text p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--white-2);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .science-text p strong { color: var(--cyan); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── Section 4: Service flow timeline ─────────────────────── */
  .process { background: var(--space); }
  .process-container { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
  .timeline {
    list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    counter-reset: step;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute;
    left: 24px; top: 12px; bottom: 12px;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cyan) 0%, rgba(100,255,218,0.2) 50%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .timeline li {
    counter-increment: step;
    position: relative;
    padding: 22px 0 22px 76px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: baseline;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .timeline li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .timeline li::before {
    content: counter(step, decimal-leading-zero);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 22px;
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--space);
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .timeline .step-title {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 19px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .timeline .step-meta {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--white-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── Section 5: Research backing ──────────────────────────── */
  .research {
    background: var(--space-2);
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .research-container { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .research-tag {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin: 0 0 56px;
  }
  .logos {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
  }
  .logo-cell {
    background: var(--space-2);
    padding: 36px 18px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    transition: background .3s ease;
  }
  .logo-cell:hover { background: var(--space-3); }
  .logo-cell .lab-name {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .logo-cell .lab-meta {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--white-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── Section 6: Bottom CTA ────────────────────────────────── */
  .cta {
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 600px at 50% 50%, rgba(100,255,218,0.10), transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(600px 400px at 30% 100%, rgba(157,78,221,0.08), transparent 60%),
      var(--space);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 160px 40px 120px;
  }
  .cta-container { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6.5vw, 80px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .cta h2 .accent { color: var(--cyan); }
  .cta-sub {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--white-2); font-size: 16px;
    margin: 0 0 48px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .signup {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .signup input {
    flex: 1; min-width: 220px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color .2s ease;
  }
  .signup input::placeholder { color: var(--white-3); }
  .signup input:focus { border-color: var(--cyan); }
  .signup button {
    background: var(--cyan);
    color: var(--space);
    border: 1px solid var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 16px 26px;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .25s ease;
  }
  .signup button:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  /* ── Footer ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  footer {
    background: var(--space);
    padding: 36px 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--white-3);
  }
  footer .copy { letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  footer .links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
  footer a { color: var(--white-3); text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--cyan); }

  /* ── Reveal on scroll ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity .9s ease, transform .9s ease; }
  .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

  /* ── Responsive ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 14px 20px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 80px 22px; }
    .hero { padding: 110px 22px 60px; }
    .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .science-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .signup { flex-direction: column; }
    .signup input, .signup button { width: 100%; }
    .timeline li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding-left: 64px; }
    .timeline::before { left: 19px; }
    .timeline li::before { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 12px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a class="brand" href="#hero">
    <svg class="brand-mark" viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"/>
      <path d="M 22 16 C 22 22, 42 22, 42 32 C 42 42, 22 42, 22 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <path d="M 42 16 C 42 22, 22 22, 22 32 C 22 42, 42 42, 42 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <line x1="22" y1="16" x2="42" y2="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      <line x1="22" y1="32" x2="42" y2="32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      <line x1="22" y1="48" x2="42" y2="48" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/>
    </svg>
    <span>AeonCircle</span>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#hero">Home</a>
    <a href="#system">AI System</a>
    <a href="#science">Biology</a>
    <a href="#process">Health Data</a>
    <a href="#research">Research</a>
    <a href="#cta" class="login">Login</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ═══════ Section 1: Hero ═══════ -->
<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="dna-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1600 900" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
      <g>
        <path class="strand"   d="M 0 200 C 200 100, 400 300, 600 200 C 800 100, 1000 300, 1200 200 C 1400 100, 1600 300, 1800 200"/>
        <path class="strand"   d="M 0 200 C 200 300, 400 100, 600 200 C 800 300, 1000 100, 1200 200 C 1400 300, 1600 100, 1800 200"/>
        <path class="strand-2" d="M 0 700 C 200 600, 400 800, 600 700 C 800 600, 1000 800, 1200 700 C 1400 600, 1600 800, 1800 700"/>
        <path class="strand-2" d="M 0 700 C 200 800, 400 600, 600 700 C 800 800, 1000 600, 1200 700 C 1400 800, 1600 600, 1800 700"/>
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="cells" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="cell" style="left: 8%;  animation-duration: 24s; animation-delay: 0s;"></span>
    <span class="cell" style="left: 22%; animation-duration: 30s; animation-delay: 4s;"></span>
    <span class="cell" style="left: 36%; animation-duration: 28s; animation-delay: 8s;"></span>
    <span class="cell" style="left: 54%; animation-duration: 34s; animation-delay: 2s;"></span>
    <span class="cell" style="left: 70%; animation-duration: 26s; animation-delay: 12s;"></span>
    <span class="cell" style="left: 84%; animation-duration: 32s; animation-delay: 6s;"></span>
    <span class="cell" style="left: 92%; animation-duration: 38s; animation-delay: 10s;"></span>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow"><span class="pulse"></span><span>AI · Longevity · Now Forming</span></p>
    <h1>Live to <span class="with-ai">120</span><br/>with AI</h1>
    <p class="hero-zh">用 AI，抵达 120 岁生命边界</p>
    <p class="hero-sub">AI 全周期生命监测 ｜ 基因优化 ｜ 代谢调控 ｜ 衰老逆转 ｜ 个性化延寿方案</p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="#cta">Start Your Life Extension <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="#system">了解 AI 延寿体系</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-cue">Scroll</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ Section 2: AI System (3 cards) ═══════ -->
<section id="system" class="system">
  <div class="system-container">
    <p class="section-eyebrow reveal">// 01 — Core System</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">AI-Driven<br/><span class="accent">Longevity System</span></h2>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card reveal">
        <svg class="card-icon" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round">
